    "Sustainable digital innovation and transformation can be fostered when SMEs modify their business models to take advantage of digital platforms (Yousaf et al., 2021).",
    "In order to endure and achieve sustained prosperity in the current era of abundant information, small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) must embrace and execute digital strategies.",
    "Digital strategy execution entails the implementation of digital technology across multiple business domains to maximize efficiency, minimize expenses, stimulate innovation, and improve customer experiences.",
    "Research has demonstrated that the implementation of digital strategies has a positive impact on both production efficiency and profitability.",
    "These methods also substantially impact successful customer relationship management, enhancing customer loyalty and satisfaction."
